### For üçé macOS

**Requirements:** Python 3 (pre-installed on macOS 10.15+)

**Installation:**

# Clone or download
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/rose-server.git
cd rose-server

# Run (no installation needed!)
python3 rose_server.py
```

**First Time Setup:**
 macOS might ask for permission to access folders
 Click "Allow" when prompted
 If you get a security warning, go to System Preferences ‚Üí Security & Privacy ‚Üí Click "Open Anyway"

Do all the above things and Enjoy ...üòé!!!


